          <p>Security is at the forefront of every app we build. We implement industry-standard encryption, secure authentication, and rigorous data protection practices to safeguard your users' information at every layer of the application.</p>
          <p>From secure API communication to compliant data storage, our team proactively identifies vulnerabilities and builds safeguards before they become issues, giving you and your users peace of mind.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tab-panel" data-panel="2">
          <p>Our apps are built to grow with your business. We design architectures that handle increasing user loads, data volumes, and feature sets without compromising performance or reliability.</p>
          <p>Whether you're launching to a handful of users or scaling to millions, our cloud-ready infrastructure and modular codebases ensure your app can expand smoothly as your needs evolve.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tab-panel" data-panel="3">
